<h2><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=Formal_fallacy&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1" title="Edit section: Common examples">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">Common examples</span></h2>
<div class="rellink noprint relarticle mainarticle">Main article: <a href="/wiki/List_of_fallacies" title="List of fallacies">List of fallacies</a></div>
