<ul>
<li><a href="http://www.virtuescience.com/logicalfallacies.html" class="external text" title="http://www.virtuescience.com/logicalfallacies.html" rel="nofollow">Logical Fallacies — a semi-ordered list with definitions</a></li>
<li><a href="http://www.fallacyfiles.org/" class="external text" title="http://www.fallacyfiles.org/" rel="nofollow">The Fallacy Files</a> by <a href="http://www.fallacyfiles.org/aboutgnc.html" class="external text" title="http://www.fallacyfiles.org/aboutgnc.html" rel="nofollow">Gary N. Curtis</a> — real examples posted regularly.</li>
<li><a href="http://esgs.free.fr/uk/logic.htm" class="external text" title="http://esgs.free.fr/uk/logic.htm" rel="nofollow">ESGE Logical Fallacies — European Society for General Semantics</a></li>
<li><a href="http://www.logicalfallacies.info/" class="external text" title="http://www.logicalfallacies.info/" rel="nofollow">Logical Fallacies .Info</a></li>
<li>Bruce Thompson's <a href="http://www.cuyamaca.edu/bruce.thompson/Fallacies/intro_fallacies.asp" class="external text" title="http://www.cuyamaca.edu/bruce.thompson/Fallacies/intro_fallacies.asp" rel="nofollow">Fallacy Page</a></li>
<li><a href="http://onegoodmove.org/fallacy/welcome.htm" class="external text" title="http://onegoodmove.org/fallacy/welcome.htm" rel="nofollow">Stephen Downes Guide to the Logical Fallacies</a></li>
<li><a href="http://www.csun.edu/~dgw61315/fallacies.html" class="external text" title="http://www.csun.edu/~dgw61315/fallacies.html" rel="nofollow">Logical Fallacies and the Art of Debate</a></li>
<li><a href="http://www.emse.fr/%7Eyukna/gmat/Logicalfallacies.html" class="external text" title="http://www.emse.fr/%7Eyukna/gmat/Logicalfallacies.html" rel="nofollow">Logical Fallacies Quiz</a> Ten common fallacies in an interactive test format.</li>
<li><a href="http://www.nizkor.org/features/fallacies/" class="external text" title="http://www.nizkor.org/features/fallacies/" rel="nofollow">42 informal logical fallacies explained by Dr. Michael C. Labossiere, including examples.</a></li>
<li><a href="http://www.fecundity.com/pmagnus/fallacies.html" class="external text" title="http://www.fecundity.com/pmagnus/fallacies.html" rel="nofollow">On Informal Fallacies</a> is a collection of one-off fallacies coined for specific, rhetorical purposes.</li>
<li><a href="http://www.marilynvossavant.com/articles/logic.html" class="external text" title="http://www.marilynvossavant.com/articles/logic.html" rel="nofollow">Marilyn vos Savant explains Logical Fallacies</a></li>
<li><a href="http://www.paradoxes.co.uk" class="external text" title="http://www.paradoxes.co.uk" rel="nofollow">Some paradoxes — an anthology</a></li>
